18... fxe6 19. Bxc6 Nxe3
{ A nice in-between move preventing White from castling, which was necessary. }
20. fxe3 { This will lead to a strong attack for Black. } 20... Qxe3+ 21. Ne2
Qd2+
{ Our queen was under attack, so this check is necessary before capturing the bishop. }
22. Kf2 bxc6
{ After having regained one of the sacrificed pieces we still have a fierce attack. With  23.--  Rf8+  being a huge threat White will have to defend accurately to hold this. }
