20. Bxd1 Ne4 21. Qe1
{ The situation has finally calmed down a bit, and White is preparing to play Bd2-Bc3. Although White has managed to exchange a couple of pieces which generally favours him, we have managed to get our pieces to more active squares in the meantime. }
21... Qd6
{ As White has moved their queen to e1, the queenside is getting more vulnerable. By playing Qd6 we intend to play Qf6 next to make Bd2-Bc3 more difficult. }
