15. Bf3 b4 16. Ne4 { This feels more natural to me than Nce2. } 16... Nxe4 17.
Bxe4 Bb5
{ The bishop prevents White from castling, which means that White needs to play Ne2. Apart from that we are also clearing the d-file to kick away the queen from d2. Once it is removed, b3+ will become quite annoying. }
18. Ne2 Rd8 19. Qc1 b3+
