{ A clever move in a way, intending to trade the c3-pawn for the b7-pawn. However, it really is time for White to finish development. }
17... Qxc3+ { We can just take it, as White should not be taking on b7. } 18.
Qxc3 Rxc3 19. Rxb7 O-O
{ We have now finished our development, while White still has the king in the centre, bishop on f1 and rook on h1. With Rc1+ incoming our initiative is just very strong. }
