{ This seems like a move that White should consider, but also one that White should reject. }
13... Qa5+
{ Allowing White to win a piece with b4, but we are intending to sacrifice on b4. }
14. b4 Nxb4 15. axb4 Bxb4+ 16. Nd2 Bxa4
{ There are multiple winning lines, but this just wins back the sacrificed material on the spot with a winning position due to  17.Rxa4  Bxd2+  . }
