so recommended in the V for von Hennig-Schara course on Chessable. However, it turns out, that the modern engines are now saying that 10...Nc6 is fine again! 10...Nc6 is the concrete approach here, while 10...Qc7 will probably lead to  more typical Schara Gambit positions. }
