19... Nxe5 20. Nf6+ { This move forces a draw. } 20... Kg7
{ 21.Nh5+  Kg8  22.Nf6+  is an immediate repetition, while after  22.Qxe5  we play  22...Bb4+  just like we do after 21. Qxe5. }
21. Qxe5 Bb4+
{ Now we force it ourselves as White refused the draw after 21. Nh5+. } 22.
axb4 Qxb4+ 23. Ke2 Qc4+ { With a draw by repetition. } *

