{ Now at least the queen is not getting forked as it was in the 23. Qf5 line. However, if we play Nxd4 exd4 Qxd4 in certain positions we are attacking the queen this time. }
23... Qxa1+ 24. Ke2 Nxd4+ 25. exd4 Kg7
{ 24...Kg7 was also a possibility, but I made sure to include the 23. Qe4 line because I saw that we need to make this slightly counterintuitive move to force the draw. }
26. Nh5+ Kg8
{ White has nothing better than to force the draw with  27.Nf6+  ,  as we are about to play Qxd4. }
