17. Bb2
{ After this move we can force the queen sacrifice again that we will see after 14. b4. Compared to that line, however, we have now also included Bb2 and Bb6, which should slightly favour White. }
17... Nxf3+
{ If you do not want to go for this forcing sequence,  17...Bg4  also seems playable. Perhaps even  17...Neg4  after which we constantly threaten to sacrifice on e3 or f2 is playable. }
18. Bxf3 Bb5 19. Nxb5 Rxd1 20. Raxd1
